#. module: website_forum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website_forum.mark_as_offensive
msgid ""
"If you close this post, it will be hidden for most users. Only\n"
"            users having a high karma can see closed posts to moderate\n"
"            them."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານປິດໂພສນີ້, ມັນຈະຖືກເຊື່ອງໄວ້ຈາກຜູ້ໃຊ້ສ່ວນໃຫຍ່. ມີພຽງ\n"
"            ຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ມີຄະແນນຊື່ສຽງສູງເທົ່ານັ້ນທີ່ສາມາດເຫັນໂພສທີ່ປິດແລ້ວ ເພື່ອກວດສອບ\n"
"            ພວກມັນໄດ້."

#. module: website_forum
#: model_terms:forum.forum,faq:website_forum.forum_help
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website_forum.default_faq
msgid ""
"If you fit in one of these example or if your motivation for asking the "
"question is “I would like to participate in a discussion about ______”, then"
" you should not be asking here but on our mailing lists. However, if your "
"motivation is “I would like others to explain ______ to me”, then you are "
"probably OK."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານຕົກຢູ່ໃນຕົວຢ່າງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ ຫຼື ຖ້າເຫດຜົນໃນການຖາມຂອງທ່ານຄື “ຂ້ອຍຢາກມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມໃນການສົນທະນາກ່ຽວກັບ "
"______”, ທ່ານບໍ່ຄວນຖາມຢູ່ນີ້ ແຕ່ຄວນໄປຖາມໃນ mailing lists ຂອງພວກເຮົາ. ເຖິງຢ່າງໃດກໍຕາມ, ຖ້າເ"
"ຫດຜົນຂອງທ່ານຄື “ຂ້ອຍຢາກໃຫ້ຄົນອື່ນອະທິບາຍ ______ ໃຫ້ຂ້ອຍ”, ທ່ານກໍສາມາດຖາມຢູ່ນີ້ໄດ້."

#. module: website_forum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:website_forum.mark_as_offensive
